DATA_OBJECT_DESCRIPTION: A data object is a collection of one or more data points that create meaning as a whole. Values in a data object may have their own unique IDs, data types, and attributes.
SELECT_CATEGORY_TO_VIEW_DATA_OBJECTS: Select a Category to view Data Objects
CATEGORY_DESCRIPTION: Categories are created in order to group Data Objects, in such a way that the Data Objects of each category are similar to each other in some way. It defines a default flow, which you can also refer while creating any new asset.
SELECT_CATEGORY_DATA_OBJECT: Select a Category/Data Object to view further

SELECT_PROCESS_TO_VIEW_DATA_OBJECTS: Select a process to view Data Objects
SELECT_PROJECT_TO_VIEW_LIST_OF_APPLICATI: Select a Project to view list of Applications/Surveys
SELECT_APPLICATION_TO_VIEW_DATA_OBJECTS: Select an Application to view Data Objects
PROJECT_DESCRIPTION: Projects are created in order to group Processes, in such a way that the processes of each Project are similar to each other in some way. It defines a default flow, which you can also refer while creating any new asset.
PROCESS_DESCRIPTION: Processes are created in order to group Data Objects, in such a way that the Data Objects of each process are similar to each other in some way. It defines a default flow, which you can also refer while creating any new asset.
APPLICATION_DESCRIPTION: Aplications are created in order to group Data Objects, in such a way that the Data Objects of each application are similar to each other in some way. It defines a default flow, which you can also refer while creating any new asset.
SEARCH_DESCRIPTION: You can select any of the search result(s).On selection,system will take you to the content of that specific page.
SEARCH_DESC_HEADING: In case you do not find your search result, you can do either of the following:
SEARCH_DESC1: May be you are looking for something in Processes or Applications Tab.
SEARCH_DESC2: Broaden your search by using fewer or more general words.
SEARCH_DESC4: You may also check Pinned or Draft assets, if it's present inside those.
